  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested help creating a meaningful acronym for a WhatsApp group to support his mother Maïta in her new life phase. Manus provided 5 curated acronym suggestions (MAÏTA, TEAM, MATA, CARE, MAM) with explanations and promised a detailed document with implementation guidance. Session ended abruptly with user saying 'Go' and Manus offering general assistance.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser wants to organize family/friends support for his mother through a WhatsApp group with a meaningful acronym name\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nGenerated 5 acronym options using mother's name (Maïta) and support concepts, with explanations for each choice\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [recommendation] Acronym suggestions — 5 curated acronym options for WhatsApp group\n- [document] Support group guide — Promised detailed document with implementation guidance\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Selected 5 best acronym options from broader set\n- Prioritized personal connection using mother's name\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Personal approach using mother's name\n- Multiple options provided\n- Clear explanations for each acronym\nFailed / suboptimal:\n\n- Session ended abruptly before user feedback\n- Document delivery unclear\nDiscoveries:\n\n- MAÏTA acronym works naturally in French\n- Balance needed between personal and universal appeal\n\n## Challenges & Blockers\n\n- Session terminated before user selection\n- No confirmation of preferred acronym\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- Which acronym does user prefer?\n- Was the document actually delivered?\n- What was user's intent with 'Go' response?\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Await user's acronym preference\n- Provide detailed implementation guide\n- Assist with group setup if requested\n---\nUID: o8M6QRAWLHCiCtqVdd5RVm | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0121\n"
